    "(3) THUMOS'14 (Jiang et al. 2014) THUMOS'14 originated from the THUMOS Challenge 2014.",
    "This dataset contains many untrimmed videos of human behaviour in real-world environments, and the ability to predict activity in untrimmed video sequences can be evaluated.",
    "The main tasks are action recognition and sequential action detection.",
    "Currently, most papers use this dataset for testing and evaluation.",
    "In the action recognition task, the training set contains 13,320 trimmed videos, covering 101 action categories."
